title: [Proposal] Increase AAVE capTier from cap4 to cap5 (30M -> 100M)
body:
This proposal also appears on [Balancer's forum](https://forum.balancer.finance/t/proposal-increase-aave-captier-from-cap4-to-cap5-30m-100m/1115).

After only 10 days being live, the liquidity on the Aave Balancer-based Safety Module has steadily grow up to ~$220M. Volume has also kept the pace of liquidity and during the last days, AAVE/WETH 80/20 is the pool with the highest daily volume across all Balancer.
With more liquidity at stake, the rewards on the Aave Safety Module went down, but keeping in good levels of ~40% APY.

Taking into account the previous numbers, we propose to raise the liquidity mining cap from $30M (cap4) to $100M (cap5) for $AAVE, following the previous raise approved on [Snapshot](https://vote.balancer.finance/#/balancer/proposal/QmPvwgUBWVVAxYnPD8cBfe3NUgfWCo32kiYQUkMF2Ktc3n).
